&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bevi is on a mission to transform how beverages are delivered and consumed. Our connected beverage platform eliminates the need for single-use bottles and cans, making it easy, fun, and sustainable to stay hydrated. As the category leader in IoT-enabled beverage technology, we&#39;re building a future where Bevi machines are everywhere people live, work, and connect. We&#39;ve raised over $160M in venture capital, serve thousands of customers across the US, Canada, UK and Ireland, and we&#39;ve been rapidly growing year over year, saving over 1 billion bottles from waste. In addition to driving hypergrowth with our current product line, Bevi is heavily investing in new product development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a National Partnership Manager to join our team. In this role, you’ll own strategic relationships with our corporate partners. You will build, strengthen, and revive partnerships that are critical to Bevi’s growth. You’ll ensure partners are successful from onboarding to activation, and help scale programs and incentives that drive long-term impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Day to Day&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships with senior decision-makers at contract foodservice companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evangelize Bevi throughout our foodservice contractor partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all expectations from sector partners are met, including achieving sales goals, adhering to service level agreements, and promptly processing orders or troubleshooting issues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement sales strategies that identify growth levers, partnership opportunities, and expansion strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Quarterly Business Reviews and annual business plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure partner enablement activities, including onboarding, training and education, off-boarding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Bevi at customer visits, relevant tradeshows and brand awareness events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of high-performance sales experience within fast-growth environments. Foodservice contractor experience is a must&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Communication &amp;amp; Presentation skills are a must. Strategic/Analytical thinker.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of building new and expanding existing partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent with CRM systems, e.g. Salesforce. Network of contacts are a plus too!&lt;/li&gt;
