&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bevi is on a mission to transform how beverages are delivered and consumed. Our connected beverage platform eliminates the need for single-use bottles and cans, making it easy, fun, and sustainable to stay hydrated. As the category leader in IoT-enabled beverage technology, we&#39;re building a future where Bevi machines are everywhere people live, work, and connect. We&#39;ve raised over $160M in venture capital, serve thousands of customers across the US, Canada, UK and Ireland, and we&#39;ve been rapidly growing year over year, saving over 1 billion bottles from waste. In addition to driving hypergrowth with our current product line, Bevi is heavily investing in new product development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is not a maintenance role. It’s a launch role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Product Manager to lead one of Bevi’s highest-priority hardware initiatives from the ground up: taking a next-generation product from development through market launch. You’ll be the connective tissue between engineering, design, operations, and commercial teams, and the person accountable for making sure we ship something customers love on time and at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll report to our Director of Product, Hardware and work closely with cross-functional leads across the business. This is a rare opportunity to own a major product arc at a company that’s already a category leader, and to have a visible, lasting impact on where Bevi goes next.&lt;/p&gt;
