&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate ambiguous business challenges into clear requirements, user stories, and scalable system designs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead working sessions, process discovery workshops, and solution design reviews with cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with EA Business Analysts on solution delivery — BA owns stakeholder discovery, process design, and requirements intake; this role owns system architecture, configuration, and build. Coordinate with RevOps on GTM process ownership, translating their operational requirements and reporting needs into Salesforce and adjacent platform solutions without duplicating RevOps&#39; analytical and process governance responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AI-First Solution Design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and deploy AI-powered workflows and agents across the revenue tech stack – from lead qualification and forecasting assistance to automated insights and CRM data enrichment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-ROI opportunities for AI and automation to reduce manual work, improve data quality, and accelerate revenue cycles; own CI/CD pipeline standards and deployment practices (Gearset) to ensure reliable, auditable releases across all Salesforce environments&lt;/li&gt;
